  "steps": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons oil in a non-stick kadai, add prawns, ¼ teaspoon turmeric powder, ½ teaspoon red chilli powder and salt, mix well and sauté on high heat for 2-3 minutes. Drain and set aside in a bowl.",
    "Heat 2 tablespoons oil in the same kadai, add cumin seeds and once they start to change colour, add garlic, mix and sauté till golden brown.",
    "Add onion, mix and sauté till golden brown. Add green chillies and mix well.",
    "Add ½ teaspoon turmeric powder, 1 teaspoon red chilli powder, coriander powder, cumin powder, garam masala powder and mix well.",
    "Add sorrel leaves, mix well and sauté for 2-3 minutes. Add ½ cup water, mix well and cook for 4-5 minutes.",
    "Add sauteed prawns and curry leaves, mix well and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Transfer into a serving bowl, garnish with slit green chilli and serve hot."
  ],
